desc_long								关于这款游戏							The sun has set at the Peggle Institute, but the bouncy delight has just begun! Join the Peggle Masters on a dreamtime adventure of alter egos and peg-tastic action. Stay up late to aim, shoot and clear orange pegs, and bask in Extreme Fever glory under the silver moon. Then, put your Peggle skills to the ultimate test in Challenge mode. If you can master all that fevered action, play to your heart's content with Duel mode and Quick Play. Plus, you can stock your Trophy Room and revel in clickable replays for even more rebounding joy!                    					                    					Explore all 60 levels in Adventure mode                    					Meet a new Peggle Master and learn a new Magic Power                    					Test your skills in 60 challenges                    					Unlock Duel mode to compete against friends and the computer                    					Celebrate your Peggle prowess with clickable replays and a Trophy Room!                                        						
